quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  96,1,"Karem ne f Soab ning sẽn naan-a wã yʋʋre."
  96,2,"A naana ninsaal n yi zɩ-pelle."
  96,3,"Karem, tɩ fo Soabã n yɩɩd ne kũuni."
  96,4,"Sẽn wilg-a gʋlsg ne kaal-moogã."
  96,5,"A wilga ninsaal bũmb ning a sẽn pa mi."
  96,6,"Ka woto ye, ad ninsaal yaa kεdgda."
  96,7,"A sã n yã t'a seka a menga."
  96,8,"Ad lεbengã pata f Soabã nengẽ."
  96,9,"F yãɑ yel-solemd sẽn le yɩɩd ned ning(Abʋʋgεhl) sẽn gɩdgde."
  96,10,"Yambã (Mʋhɑmmɑd) t'a sã n wa pʋʋsdẽ?"
  96,11,"Fo yãame sã n mikɑme t'ɑ sẽn gɩdgd-ɑ wã sã n bee kãndgr zugu."
  96,12,"Ma a sagla ne wẽn-zoεεga?"
  96,13,"F yãame tɩ gɩdgdã sã n yagsame n gõd a zãn-kuidga."
  96,14,"Rẽ yĩnga a pa bãng tɩ Wẽnd nee ɑ sẽn tʋmdã?"
  96,15,"Pa woto ye! Lak t'a sã n pa tek n bas, D na n veo-ɑ-la ne rĩirã zoobdẽ."
  96,16,"Pʋ-yagd sẽn yaa tudgd rĩir zoobdo."
  96,17,"Bɩ a bool a zĩ-zĩidsẽ rãmba."
  96,18,"Tõnd na n boola D tãp-biisã."
  96,19,"Pa woto ye! Ra tũ-a ye, la f tugli (maan suguudu) la f bao pẽnegre."
